posting_body: ['For leasing info call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!', 'Ask about ID#73080', 'Nestled on six acres in the prestigious Galleria area of Houston, this community places you in the center of it all.', 'From sunlit tropical environments to luxurious master suites with large walk-in closets, these apartments reflect an outstanding quality of life.', 'Come make your home with us in the luxurious Uptown area, where international shopping and world class restaurants are within walking distance from your front door.', 'The exterior of the apartment features rock and stucco masonry with a Mediterranean courtyard feel and lush landscaping and water features throughout.', 'Unique interior features include granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, slate tile flooring, crown molding and elegant archways and alcoves.', 'A serene palm surrounded pool, newly renovated fitness center with sauna, 24 hour courtesy patrol and onsite dry-cleaning pick-up and delivery are a few of the amenities that welcome you.', 'Community Amenities', 'Controlled access gate with 24 onsite courtesy office', 'Serene pool with sundeck', 'Valet trash door to door trash pick up', 'Complimentary Wi-Fi access in common areas', 'Multi level parking garage with direct access', '24 hour emergency maintenance', 'Dry cleaning pick up and drop off', 'Courtyards with grills', 'Elevators', 'Fitness Center', 'Fitness classes', 'Free Weights', 'Spa/Hot Tub', 'Sauna', 'Recycling', 'Package Receiving', 'Night Patrol']
